Credit Suisse Asset Management, LLC: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 28, 2017 6:40 AM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of Credit Suisse Asset Management, LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Credit Suisse Asset Management, LLC is a privately owned investment manager. It provides its services to charitable organizations, governments and governmental agencies, supranational organizations, high net worth individuals, public and private pension plans, sovereign wealth funds, corporations, registered investment companies and private funds. The firm manages separate client-focused equity and fixed income portfolios. It manages equity, fixed income, and balanced mutual funds. The firm also manages hedge funds. It also makes private equity investments in the financial technology sector and fund of fund investments in private equity funds. The firm invests in public equity, fixed income,...
Credit Suisse Asset Management, LLC is a privately owned investment manager. It provides its services to charitable organizations, governments and governmental agencies, supranational organizations, high net worth individuals, public and private pension plans, sovereign wealth funds, corporations, registered investment companies and private funds. The firm manages separate client-focused equity and fixed income portfolios. It manages equity, fixed income, and balanced mutual funds. The firm also manages hedge funds. It also makes private equity investments in the financial technology sector and fund of fund investments in private equity funds. The firm invests in public equity, fixed income, and alternative investment markets across the globe. It primarily invests in stocks of companies across all market capitalization. For fixed income, the firm invests in government and corporate securities. It employs combination of fundamental and quantitative analysis along with bottom-up approach to create its portfolios. Credit Suisse Asset Management, LLC is was founded in 1999 and is based in New York City with additional offices in San Francisco, California; Research Triangle Park, North Carolina; and Chicago, Illinois. Credit Suisse Asset Management, LLC operates as a subsidiary of Credit Suisse Asset Management (Switzerland)
Detailed Description


One Madison AvenueNew York, NY 10010-3629United StatesFounded in 1999



Phone: 212-325-2000

