Credit Suisse Asset Management, LLC Key Developments

Credit Suisse Asset Management, LLC Presents at 6th Annual Investors' Conference on CLOS and Leveraged Loans, May-24-2017 04:45 PM
May 21 17
Credit Suisse Asset Management, LLC Presents at 6th Annual Investors' Conference on CLOS and Leveraged Loans, May-24-2017 04:45 PM. Venue: Conrad New York, 102 North End Avenue, New York, NY 10282, United States. Speakers: Amir Vardi, Managing Director, Structured Products Portfolio Manager.


Credit Suisse Asset Management Unveils New Trend-Tracking Fund
Jan 25 17
Credit Suisse Asset Management has launched a new liquid alternatives fund that aims to generate positive returns by exploiting trends on various markets and investment classes. The  new UCITS-compliant Luxembourg-domiciled vehicle, known as the Credit Suisse (Lux) Multi-Trend Fund, aims to generate positive returns in markets of falling and rising equity, bond, currency and commodity prices. It will invest in highly liquid and widely available instruments including index or currency futures and observes short-, medium- and long-term trends. The new fund is approved for distribution in Switzerland, Germany, Austria, Italy, France, the Netherlands  and the UK.


Credit Suisse Asset Management, LLC Presents at 8th annual Southeast Asia Institutional Investment Forum, Nov-30-2016 02:05 PM
Nov 28 16
Credit Suisse Asset Management, LLC Presents at 8th annual Southeast Asia Institutional Investment Forum, Nov-30-2016 02:05 PM. Venue: Ritz Carlton, Singapore. Speakers: Alexandre Bouchardy, Head Fixed Income Asia.


